---
name: ⚖️ 负载均衡拓展
desc: 使用 filter 筛选器兼容提取所有主订阅节点
proxy-groups:
  - name: ⚖️ 负载均衡-散列
    type: load-balance
    url: http://www.gstatic.com/generate_204
    interval: 150
    strategy: consistent-hashing
    filter: .*
  - name: ⚖️ 负载均衡-轮询
    type: load-balance
    url: http://www.gstatic.com/generate_204
    interval: 150
    strategy: round-robin
    filter: .*
  - name: 🚀 节点选择
    type: select
    proxies:
      - ⚖️ 负载均衡-散列
      - ⚖️ 负载均衡-轮询
